<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “伊坦，再见！希望你的第一天玩儿得开心！” 弗里克老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦走进体育馆时，他挥了挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “你一定是伊坦。” 雪莉老师微笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“欢迎来到儿童中心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦看到两个女生在交换珠子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们抬头看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个男生在打篮球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也停下来看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “新同学？” 一个男生说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “伊坦，这是尼娜和莉琪。她们在三年级。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是波比和贾森，他们在四年级，和你一样！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伊坦刚从加利福尼亚州搬过来。” 雪莉老师告诉大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好。” 男生们一起说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你晒得很黑。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “南加利福尼亚州一年到头都温暖晴朗。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦看着窗外，皱了皱眉头。“不像这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要做儿童中心剪贴簿！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们每天都有新活动。” 她告诉伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “很有意思！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “今天我们要做一本剪贴簿，你可以在这一年里填写。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，选一张长卡纸作为剪贴簿的封面和背面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对折后在前面写上年份和 ‘儿童中心’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 贾森和波比选了橙色。但是伊坦选了蓝色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我最喜欢蓝色，因为这是大海的颜色。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在加利福尼亚，我每天放学都去冲浪！” 他停了一下，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是宾夕法尼亚没有海。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “但是，宾夕法尼亚有其他有趣的事可以做。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “现在选六张小一点的纸作内页。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把它们放进封皮里，用订书机订住折好的那一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在第一页贴上‘我的信息’表。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最喜欢的食物是墨西哥卷饼！” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会在儿童中心做墨西哥卷饼吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “是啊！我们做墨西哥卷饼吧！” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许吧。我们经常做好吃的。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下一页是九月的页面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用这些贴纸在上面拼出 ‘九月’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个月你们可以画画或者写下学校里发生的事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我要写关于伊坦的事。他是一个穿着蓝色短裤的新同学。” 莉琪说。她指了指伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “用手指别人是不礼貌的，莉琪。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我要写我在儿童中心的第一天。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你们的想法都很好！接下来的每一页是一个月，直到六月。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以在这一年里把其他页填写好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，多出了一页，是用来干什么的？” 伊坦问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一页是 ‘朋友页’。我们可以互相签名！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个想法太酷了。” 伊坦笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以在我的剪贴簿上签名吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “当然了。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “大家都过来，我们拍一张照片。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要放在剪贴簿的封面上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 孩子们站在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师在相机上设置了定时拍摄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她及时地跑到了孩子们身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“茄子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>